videos.description: Caleb Swanigan makes the steal and then finishes in the post to open up scoring for the Boilermakers.
videos.headline: Caleb Swanigan records the steal and the score

videos.description: Ryan Cline takes the feed from Spike Albrecht and hits the deep 3.
videos.headline: Purdue's Cline hits the deep 3

videos.description: Kenny Goins throws down the big dunk off feed from Eron Harris.
videos.headline: Kenny Goins with the big-time slam for MSU

videos.description: Issac Haas goes to work in the low post by flashing the pretty skyhook.
videos.headline: Haas showcases the textbook skyhook for Purdue

videos.description: Nick Ward rebounds his own miss and puts it back in.
videos.headline: Ward shows the extra effort for the putback for MSU

videos.description: Caleb Swanigan feeds it to the cutting Issac Haas for the dunk.
videos.headline: Isaac Haas sends in the big slam for Purdue

videos.description: Issac Haas takes the feed from P.J. Thompson and finishes at the rim.
videos.headline: Thompson dishes to Haas as Boilermakers extend their lead

videos.description: Postgame interview with Caleb Swanigan discusses how Purdue showed maturity in victory over MSU
videos.headline: Postgame interview with Caleb Swanigan discussing his 23rd double-double in 27 games in victory over MSU

videos.description: Swanigan pours in 24 points and 14 rebounds in a 80-63 win.
videos.headline: Caleb Swanigan carries Purdue past Michigan State
